                  , putting him in sear, and feloniously taking from his person and against his will, a silver watch, value 2l. and a piece of steel chain, value 6d. the goods of the said 
                     <persName id="t17950916-23-person289">
                        William
                         Ashton
                     <interp inst="t17950916-23-person289" type="surname" value="Ashton"></interp>
